This is your new Play 2.0 application
=====================================

This file will be packaged with your application, when using `play dist`.


Software needed
===============

rabbitmq
- erlang
- rabbitmq

mongo
- mongo (http://www.mongodb.org/downloads)
-- unzip

Starting up

rabbitmq:
- enable management plugin
-- rabbitmq-plugins enable rabbitmq_management
- launch rabbitmq
-- (cd ${HOME}/rabbitmq-3.0.1 && sbin/rabbitmq-server)
- connect to server
-- http://localhost:15672/

mongo:
- start mong
-- (cd ${HOME}/mongodb-2.2.2 && bin/mongod --verbose --dbpath db)

medici:
- launch sbt inside medici-play folder
-- ./sbt
- start application
-- run
- connect to server
-- http://localhost:9000/

Editing code

make medici ready for eclipse
- in sbt command line
-- eclipsify with-source=true

